title: Downtown Grocery
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Organic, Buffet, Fast food, Salad bar, Take-out
description: A local organic grocery store with a vegetarian kitchen, three bakeshops, and an everyday farmers' market offering regional, raw, natural, whole and bulk foods from farmers, producers, bakers, and cheese makers to support the regional foodshed. Serves world-inspired cuisine plus old-fashioned favorites with many vegan options.
